{"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/orderedcollections\/ordereddictionary\/subscript(_:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["Linux"],"tokens":[{"text":"subscript","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"key","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Key","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Value","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The value associated with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"type":"text","text":" if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"type":"text","text":" is in the dictionary;"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"otherwise, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The key to find in the dictionary.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"key"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"key-based","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" subscript returns the value for the given key if the key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is found in the dictionary, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if the key is not found."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following example creates a new dictionary and prints the value of a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"key found in the dictionary ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"Coral\""},{"type":"text","text":") and a key not found in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dictionary ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"Cerise\""},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["var hues: OrderedDictionary = [\"Heliotrope\": 296, \"Coral\": 16, \"Aquamarine\": 156]","print(hues[\"Coral\"])","\/\/ Prints \"Optional(16)\"","print(hues[\"Cerise\"])","\/\/ Prints \"nil\""]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When you assign a value for a key and that key already exists, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dictionary overwrites the existing value. If the dictionary doesn’t","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"contain the key, the key and value are added as a new key-value pair.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here, the value for the key "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"Coral\""},{"type":"text","text":" is updated from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"16"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"18"},{"type":"text","text":" and a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"new key-value pair is added for the key "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"Cerise\""},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["hues[\"Coral\"] = 18","print(hues[\"Coral\"])","\/\/ Prints \"Optional(18)\"","","hues[\"Cerise\"] = 330","print(hues[\"Cerise\"])","\/\/ Prints \"Optional(330)\""]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you assign ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" as the value for the given key, the dictionary","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removes that key and its associated value.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the following example, the key-value pair for the key "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"Aquamarine\""},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is removed from the dictionary by assigning "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" to the key-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subscript."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["hues[\"Aquamarine\"] = nil","print(hues)","\/\/ Prints \"[\"Coral\": 18, \"Heliotrope\": 296, \"Cerise\": 330]\""]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Looking up values in the dictionary through this subscript","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"has an expected complexity of O(1) hashing\/comparison operations on","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"average, if ","type":"text"},{"code":"Key","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implements high-quality hashing. Updating the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dictionary also has an amortized expected complexity of O(1) –","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"although individual updates may need to copy or resize the dictionary’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"underlying storage.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Complexity"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OrderedCollections\/documentation\/OrderedCollections\/OrderedDictionary\/subscript(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Accesses the value associated with the given key for reading and writing."}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OrderedCollections","symbolKind":"subscript","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"subscript"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Key"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Value"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"subscript(_:)","conformance":{"availabilityPrefix":[{"text":"Available when","type":"text"}],"conformancePrefix":[{"text":"Conforms when","type":"text"}],"constraints":[{"code":"Key","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" conforms to ","type":"text"},{"code":"Hashable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},"externalID":"s:18OrderedCollections0A10DictionaryVyq_Sgxcip","roleHeading":"Instance Subscript","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"OrderedCollections"}]},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OrderedCollections\/documentation\/OrderedCollections","doc:\/\/OrderedCollections\/documentation\/OrderedCollections\/OrderedDictionary"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":2,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://OrderedCollections/documentation/OrderedCollections/OrderedDictionary":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An ordered collection of key-value pairs."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrderedDictionary"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrderedDictionary"}],"title":"OrderedDictionary","url":"\/documentation\/orderedcollections\/ordereddictionary","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OrderedCollections\/documentation\/OrderedCollections\/OrderedDictionary"},"doc://OrderedCollections/documentation/OrderedCollections":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OrderedCollections\/documentation\/OrderedCollections","role":"collection","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/orderedcollections","title":"OrderedCollections"},"doc://OrderedCollections/documentation/OrderedCollections/OrderedDictionary/subscript(_:)":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OrderedCollections\/documentation\/OrderedCollections\/OrderedDictionary\/subscript(_:)","url":"\/documentation\/orderedcollections\/ordereddictionary\/subscript(_:)","title":"subscript(_:)","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Accesses the value associated with the given key for reading and writing."}],"fragments":[{"text":"subscript","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Key"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Value"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"conformance